* A sizable group of verbs have infinitives in {{m|ro||-i}} but do not use the infix {{m|ro||-esc-}}, and are otherwise fairly regular; these include, among others, the common verb {{m|ro|dormi|t=sleep}}, {{m|ro|simți|t=feel}}, {{m|ro|auzi|t=hear}}.
* There is a variant form, {{m|ro||-î}}, derived from the same Latin source.

