# Third-person singular possessive suffix denoting singular possession.
#: {{suffixusex|tr|ev|gloss1=house|evi|gloss2=his/her/its house}}
#: {{suffixusex|tr|ofis|gloss1=office|ofisi|gloss2=his/her/its office}}
