===Etymology 2===
From the name of musicologist [[w:Giovanni Battista Doni|Giovanni Battista '''Do'''ni]], who suggested replacing the original {{m-lite|it|ut}} with an [[open syllable]] for ease of singing. First found in {{der-lite|en|it|-}}.

