=====Usage notes=====
* Becomes {{m-lite|gd|dh'}} before a word beginning with a vowel or a lenited '''fh''' followed by a vowel.
*: {{uxi|gd|'''Dh''''fhàg an t-òran brònach mi.|The song made me sad.}}
*: {{uxi|gd|'''Dh''''òl e am pinnt.|He drank the pint.}}
*: {{uxi|gd|An '''do dh''''innis mi thu mar-thà.|Did I not already tell you.}}
* Usually omitted before a consonant except after particles such as {{m-lite|gd|an}}, {{m-lite|gd|cha}} etc.

