* {{a|Berlin-Brandenburg}} also {{IPA|de|/dɐt/|/dət/}}
* {{audio|de|De-dat.ogg|Audio}}

===Article===
{{head|de|article}}

# {{lb|de|colloquial|regional|also|_|Ruhrdeutsch}} {{alternative form of|de|das}}
#: {{ux|de|Gibste mir ma’ '''dat''' Wasser?|Could you pass me '''the''' water?}}

===Pronoun===
{{de-pron}}

# {{lb|de|colloquial|regional}} {{alternative form of|de|das}}
#: {{ux|de|'''Dat''' weiß ich nich'.|I don't know '''that'''.}}

===Pronoun===
